{
  "chapter": 20,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十回\"除夕之夜\"以两条平行线展开：丁灵琳在除夕夜陪伴重伤的郭定，郭定自知将死劝她离开，丁灵琳却主动提出嫁给他以激励其求生意志，并请老掌柜操办喜酒。与此同时，叶开在红楼与上官小仙共度除夕，上官小仙精心布置洞房场景试图拉近距离，叶开却心系丁灵琳保持距离。上官小仙透露一只以活人肉为食的黑鸽带来魔教情报：四大天王已有三人潜入长安，其中\"班察巴那\"可能就是已被杀的玉箫。叶开得知长安暗流涌动，决定伤愈后离开。章末上官小仙暗示叶开的朋友即将办喜酒，制造悬念。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "明天就过年了，外面有人在放鞭炮。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "你想不想喝碗热汤？今天晚上他们一定给你炖鸡汤。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "你想要什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "你走吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "你……你要我走？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "我知道我已不行了，你不必再陪着我。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "我一定要陪着你，看着你好起来，我知道你一定可以活下去。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "你若真的觉得自己要死了，你就对不起我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "因为……因为我已准备嫁给你。难道你要我做寡妇？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "真的？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "当然是真的。我们随时都可以成亲。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "明天就是个吉祥的好日子，我们已不必再等。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_ding",
      "speaker_name": "郭定",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "可是我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_guo_ding",
      "text": "所以你一定要活下去，一定！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "姑娘还没有睡？病人是不是已好了些？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "明天你能不能替我办十几桌酒？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "明天？明天是大年初一，恐怕……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "一定要明天，再迟，恐怕就来不及了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "姑娘要请人喝春酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "不是春酒，是喜酒。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "喜酒！难道姑娘你明天就要成亲？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "冲冲喜也好，病人一冲喜，病马上就会好的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "所以我希望这喜事能办得热闹些，越热闹越好。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "行，这件事就包在我身上。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "text": "明天晚上行不？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_zhang_gui",
      "speaker_name": "老掌柜",
      "listener": "char_ding_lin_lin",
      "text": "准定就是明天晚上。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你说这样像不像洞房？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "不像？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "什么地方不像？难道我不像新娘子？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你像新娘子，我却不像新郎。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "谁说你不像。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你为什么不去照照镜子。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "用不着照镜子，我也看得见我自己，而且看得很清楚。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我这一辈子最大的长处，就是永远都能看清我自己。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你喜不喜欢过年。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "不知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "怎么会不知道？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "没有家的人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "其实我……我一样也从来没有过过年。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你当然知道我母亲是个什么样的人，但你却永远也不会知道她晚年过的是什么样的日子，别人在过年的时候，她总是抱着我，偷偷的躲在被窝里流泪。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "同是天涯沦落人，相逢何必曾相识。其实你也该知道我们本是同样的人，你对我为什么总是这么冷淡？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "那只因你已变了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你认为我现在已变成个什么样的人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你若认为我已变得和……和她一样，你就错了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "看着我，我有话问你。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你问。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我若告诉你，我这一辈子还没有男人碰过我，你信不信？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你若以为我对别的男人，也跟对你一样，你就更错了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你……你为什么要这样对我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你心里难道还不明白？为什么还要问？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "今天是大年夜，我们为什么总是要说这种不开心的事。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为不管我说不说，你都是一样不开心的。因为我知道你心里总是在想着丁灵琳。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我跟她认识已不止一天了，她实在是个很好的女孩子，对我也一直都很好。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我对你不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你们不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "有什么不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你是个很了不起的女人，你有才能，也有野心，你还有很多事可以做，可是她……她却只有依靠我。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你是不是认为不管你到什么地方去了，不管你去了多久，她都会等你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "她一定会等。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你不信？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我只不过想提醒你，有些女人，是经不起试探的。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我相信她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你有没有听说过庄周的故事？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "他们本来也是对恩爱夫妇，可是庄周一死，他的妻子立刻就改嫁给别人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "幸好我既没有妻子，也没有庄周那么大的神通，更不会装死。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这么凶的鸽子倒真是天下少有。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这种鸽子本来就很少有，据我知道，天下一共也只有三只。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "要养这么样一只鸽子，可真不是容易事，能养得起它的人，天下也绝不超出三个。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道这种鸽子平常吃的是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我就知道你永远也想不到的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "它吃的至少总不会是人肉吧？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cui",
      "text": "小翠。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cui",
      "text": "你的刀呢？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_cui",
      "text": "很好，现在你可以喂它了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "它吃的真是人肉。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "非但是人肉，而且一定要从活人身上割下的肉，还一定要是年轻的女孩子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你知不知道这只鸽子是从哪里飞来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "它已飞了几千里路，而且还为我带来了一件很重要的消息，就算要我自己割块肉给它吃，我也愿意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "什么消息？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 390,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "魔教的消息。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "这只鸽子的主人难道是魔教的教主？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不是教主，是一位公主，很美的公主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 396
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "她怎么会跟你通消息？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 398,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为她也是人，只要是人，我就有法子收买。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 400
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "也许只有你是例外。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 402
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "难道她敢将魔教的秘密出卖给你？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "只可惜她知道的秘密并不太多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "她知道些什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她只知道魔教的四大天王中，已有三个人到了长安，却不知道他们在这里用的是什么身份。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "她也不知道这三个人的名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 414,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "就算知道也没有用，无论谁人了魔教后，都得将自己过去的一切完全放弃，连本来的名字也不能再用。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "所以她只知道这三个人在魔教中用的名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "魔教中的四大天王，名字都很绝，一个叫'牒儿布'，一个叫'多尔甲'，一个叫'布达拉'，一个叫'班察巴那'。这都是古老的藏文。'牒儿布'的意思象征着智慧，'多尔甲'的意思，象征着权法。'布达拉'是孤峰。'班察巴那'是爱欲之神。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在除了多尔甲天王还留守在魔山之外，其余的三大天王，都已到了长安。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "这消息可靠？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "绝对可靠。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你也猜不出他们是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我只想到了一个人，'班察巴那'天王，很可能就是玉箫。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你能不能从玉箫口中，问出那两个人来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "不能。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 444,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你也不能？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我就算有法子能让各种人说实话，也有一种人是例外。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "死人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "怎么死的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "有人杀了他。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 458
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "是谁杀得了东海玉箫？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 460,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "在这长安城里，能杀他的人并不止一个。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我在这里才不过十来天，长安城里却似已有了很多变化，发生了很多事。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你是不是已想走？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我的伤已好了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 470
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "伤一好就要走？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 472,
      "line_end": 472
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我迟早总是要走的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 474
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你准备什么时候走？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 476,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "明天……我若是明天走，还可以到长安城去拜拜年。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "除了拜年外，你还可以赶上一顿喜酒。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "谁的喜酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 486,
      "line_end": 486
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "当然是你的朋友，一个跟你很要好的朋友。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 20,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    }
  ],
